text: Abdullah Mokoginta (5 May 1935 â€“ 16 August 2021) was an Indonesian politician. He was Deputy Governor of North Sulawesi from 1986 to 1991. He was a member of the People's Representative Council from 1992 to 1999. Mokoginta was born in North Sulawesi, Dutch East Indies. Mokoginta died on 16 August 2021 in Kotamobagu, Indonesia at the age of 86. ==References== Category:Indonesian politicians Category:1935 births Category:2021 deaths
